  42   def createColorfulTestImage(self):
  43     ch255 = tf.fill([1, 100, 200, 1], tf.constant(255, dtype=tf.uint8))
  44     ch128 = tf.fill([1, 100, 200, 1], tf.constant(128, dtype=tf.uint8))
  45     ch0 = tf.fill([1, 100, 200, 1], tf.constant(0, dtype=tf.uint8))
  46     imr = tf.concat([ch255, ch0, ch0], 3)
  47     img = tf.concat([ch255, ch255, ch0], 3)
  48     imb = tf.concat([ch255, ch0, ch255], 3)
  49     imw = tf.concat([ch128, ch128, ch128], 3)
  50     imu = tf.concat([imr, img], 2)
  51     imd = tf.concat([imb, imw], 2)
  52     im = tf.concat([imu, imd], 1)
  53     return im
  54 
  55   def createTestImages(self):
  56     images_r = tf.constant([[[128, 128, 128, 128], [0, 0, 128, 128],
  57                              [0, 128, 128, 128], [192, 192, 128, 128]]],
  58                            dtype=tf.uint8)
  59     images_r = tf.expand_dims(images_r, 3)
  60     images_g = tf.constant([[[0, 0, 128, 128], [0, 0, 128, 128],
  61                              [0, 128, 192, 192], [192, 192, 128, 192]]],
  62                            dtype=tf.uint8)
  63     images_g = tf.expand_dims(images_g, 3)
  64     images_b = tf.constant([[[128, 128, 192, 0], [0, 0, 128, 192],
  65                              [0, 128, 128, 0], [192, 192, 192, 128]]],
  66                            dtype=tf.uint8)
  67     images_b = tf.expand_dims(images_b, 3)
  68     images = tf.concat([images_r, images_g, images_b], 3)
  69     return images

 338   def testRgbToGrayscale(self):
 339     def graph_fn():
 340       images = self.createTestImages()
 341       grayscale_images = preprocessor._rgb_to_grayscale(images)
 342       expected_images = tf.image.rgb_to_grayscale(images)
 343       return grayscale_images, expected_images
 344     (grayscale_images, expected_images) = self.execute_cpu(graph_fn, [])
 345     self.assertAllEqual(expected_images, grayscale_images)
 346 
 347   def testNormalizeImage(self):
 348     def graph_fn():

 589   def _testPreprocessorCache(self,
 590                              preprocess_options,
 591                              test_boxes=False,
 592                              test_masks=False,
 593                              test_keypoints=False):
 594     if self.is_tf2(): return
 595     def graph_fn():
 596       cache = preprocessor_cache.PreprocessorCache()
 597       images = self.createTestImages()
 598       boxes = self.createTestBoxes()
 599       weights = self.createTestGroundtruthWeights()
 600       classes = self.createTestLabels()
 601       masks = self.createTestMasks()
 602       keypoints, _ = self.createTestKeypoints()
 603       preprocessor_arg_map = preprocessor.get_default_func_arg_map(
 604           include_instance_masks=test_masks, include_keypoints=test_keypoints)
 605       out = []
 606       for _ in range(2):
 607         tensor_dict = {
 608             fields.InputDataFields.image: images,
 609             fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_weights: weights
 610         }
 611         if test_boxes:
 612           tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes] = boxes
 613           tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_classes] = classes
 614         if test_masks:
 615           tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_instance_masks] = masks
 616         if test_keypoints:
 617           tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_keypoints] = keypoints
 618         out.append(
 619             preprocessor.preprocess(tensor_dict, preprocess_options,
 620                                     preprocessor_arg_map, cache))
 621       return out
 622 
 623     out1, out2 = self.execute_cpu_tf1(graph_fn, [])
 624     for (_, v1), (_, v2) in zip(out1.items(), out2.items()):
 625       self.assertAllClose(v1, v2)
 626 
 627   def testRandomHorizontalFlip(self):
 628     def graph_fn():
 629       preprocess_options = [(preprocessor.random_horizontal_flip, {})]
 630       images = self.expectedImagesAfterNormalization()
 631       boxes = self.createTestBoxes()
 632       tensor_dict = {fields.InputDataFields.image: images,
 633                      fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes: boxes}
 634       images_expected1 = self.expectedImagesAfterLeftRightFlip()
 635       boxes_expected1 = self.expectedBoxesAfterLeftRightFlip()
 636       images_expected2 = images
 637       boxes_expected2 = boxes
 638       tensor_dict = preprocessor.preprocess(tensor_dict, preprocess_options)
 639       images = tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.image]
 640       boxes = tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes]
 641 
 642       boxes_diff1 = tf.squared_difference(boxes, boxes_expected1)
 643       boxes_diff2 = tf.squared_difference(boxes, boxes_expected2)
 644       boxes_diff = tf.multiply(boxes_diff1, boxes_diff2)
 645       boxes_diff_expected = tf.zeros_like(boxes_diff)
 646 
 647       images_diff1 = tf.squared_difference(images, images_expected1)
 648       images_diff2 = tf.squared_difference(images, images_expected2)
 649       images_diff = tf.multiply(images_diff1, images_diff2)
 650       images_diff_expected = tf.zeros_like(images_diff)
 651       return [images_diff, images_diff_expected, boxes_diff,
 652               boxes_diff_expected]
 653     (images_diff_, images_diff_expected_, boxes_diff_,
 654      boxes_diff_expected_) = self.execute_cpu(graph_fn, [])
 655     self.assertAllClose(boxes_diff_, boxes_diff_expected_)
 656     self.assertAllClose(images_diff_, images_diff_expected_)
 657

 720           include_keypoints=True,
 721           include_keypoint_visibilities=True)

 881       images = self.expectedImagesAfterNormalization()
 882       boxes = self.createEmptyTestBoxes()
 883       tensor_dict = {
 884           fields.InputDataFields.image: images,
 885           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes: boxes
 886       }
 887       images_expected1 = self.expectedImagesAfterRot90()
 888       boxes_expected = self.createEmptyTestBoxes()
 889       images_expected2 = images
 890       tensor_dict = preprocessor.preprocess(tensor_dict, preprocess_options)
 891       images = tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.image]
 892       boxes = tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes]
 893 
 894       images_diff1 = tf.squared_difference(images, images_expected1)
 895       images_diff2 = tf.squared_difference(images, images_expected2)
 896       images_diff = tf.multiply(images_diff1, images_diff2)
 897       images_diff_expected = tf.zeros_like(images_diff)
 898       return [images_diff, images_diff_expected, boxes, boxes_expected]
 899 
 900     (images_diff_, images_diff_expected_, boxes_,
 901      boxes_expected_) = self.execute_cpu(graph_fn, [])
 902     self.assertAllClose(boxes_, boxes_expected_)
 903     self.assertAllClose(images_diff_, images_diff_expected_)

1008   def testRandomRGBtoGray(self):
1009 
1010     def graph_fn():
1011       preprocess_options = [(preprocessor.random_rgb_to_gray, {})]
1012       images_original = self.createTestImages()
1013       tensor_dict = {fields.InputDataFields.image: images_original}
1014       tensor_dict = preprocessor.preprocess(tensor_dict, preprocess_options)
1015       images_gray = tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.image]
1016       images_gray_r, images_gray_g, images_gray_b = tf.split(
1017           value=images_gray, num_or_size_splits=3, axis=3)
1018       images_r, images_g, images_b = tf.split(
1019           value=images_original, num_or_size_splits=3, axis=3)
1020       images_r_diff1 = tf.squared_difference(
1021           tf.cast(images_r, dtype=tf.float32),
1022           tf.cast(images_gray_r, dtype=tf.float32))
1023       images_r_diff2 = tf.squared_difference(
1024           tf.cast(images_gray_r, dtype=tf.float32),
1025           tf.cast(images_gray_g, dtype=tf.float32))
1026       images_r_diff = tf.multiply(images_r_diff1, images_r_diff2)
1027       images_g_diff1 = tf.squared_difference(
1028           tf.cast(images_g, dtype=tf.float32),
1029           tf.cast(images_gray_g, dtype=tf.float32))
1030       images_g_diff2 = tf.squared_difference(
1031           tf.cast(images_gray_g, dtype=tf.float32),
1032           tf.cast(images_gray_b, dtype=tf.float32))
1033       images_g_diff = tf.multiply(images_g_diff1, images_g_diff2)
1034       images_b_diff1 = tf.squared_difference(
1035           tf.cast(images_b, dtype=tf.float32),
1036           tf.cast(images_gray_b, dtype=tf.float32))
1037       images_b_diff2 = tf.squared_difference(
1038           tf.cast(images_gray_b, dtype=tf.float32),
1039           tf.cast(images_gray_r, dtype=tf.float32))
1040       images_b_diff = tf.multiply(images_b_diff1, images_b_diff2)
1041       image_zero1 = tf.constant(0, dtype=tf.float32, shape=[1, 4, 4, 1])
1042       return [images_r_diff, images_g_diff, images_b_diff, image_zero1]
1043 
1044     (images_r_diff_, images_g_diff_, images_b_diff_,
1045      image_zero1_) = self.execute_cpu(graph_fn, [])
1046     self.assertAllClose(images_r_diff_, image_zero1_)
1047     self.assertAllClose(images_g_diff_, image_zero1_)
1048     self.assertAllClose(images_b_diff_, image_zero1_)
1049

1544   def testRandomCropImageWithMultiClassScores(self):
1545     def graph_fn():
1546       preprocessing_options = []
1547       preprocessing_options.append((preprocessor.normalize_image, {
1548           'original_minval': 0,
1549           'original_maxval': 255,
1550           'target_minval': 0,
1551           'target_maxval': 1
1552       }))
1553       preprocessing_options.append((preprocessor.random_crop_image, {}))
1554       images = self.createTestImages()
1555       boxes = self.createTestBoxes()
1556       labels = self.createTestLabels()
1557       weights = self.createTestGroundtruthWeights()
1558       multiclass_scores = self.createTestMultiClassScores()
1559 
1560       tensor_dict = {
1561           fields.InputDataFields.image: images,
1562           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes: boxes,
1563           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_classes: labels,
1564           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_weights: weights,
1565           fields.InputDataFields.multiclass_scores: multiclass_scores
1566       }
1567       distorted_tensor_dict = preprocessor.preprocess(tensor_dict,
1568                                                       preprocessing_options)
1569       distorted_images = distorted_tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.image]
1570       distorted_boxes = distorted_tensor_dict[
1571           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes]
1572       distorted_multiclass_scores = distorted_tensor_dict[
1573           fields.InputDataFields.multiclass_scores]
1574       boxes_rank = tf.rank(boxes)
1575       distorted_boxes_rank = tf.rank(distorted_boxes)
1576       images_rank = tf.rank(images)
1577       distorted_images_rank = tf.rank(distorted_images)
1578       multiclass_scores_rank = tf.rank(multiclass_scores)
1579       distorted_multiclass_scores_rank = tf.rank(distorted_multiclass_scores)
1580       return [
1581           boxes_rank, distorted_boxes, distorted_boxes_rank, images_rank,
1582           distorted_images_rank, multiclass_scores_rank,
1583           distorted_multiclass_scores_rank, distorted_multiclass_scores
1584       ]
1585 
1586     (boxes_rank_, distorted_boxes_, distorted_boxes_rank_, images_rank_,
1587      distorted_images_rank_, multiclass_scores_rank_,
1588      distorted_multiclass_scores_rank_,
1589      distorted_multiclass_scores_) = self.execute_cpu(graph_fn, [])
1590     self.assertAllEqual(boxes_rank_, distorted_boxes_rank_)
1591     self.assertAllEqual(images_rank_, distorted_images_rank_)
1592     self.assertAllEqual(multiclass_scores_rank_,
1593                         distorted_multiclass_scores_rank_)
1594     self.assertAllEqual(distorted_boxes_.shape[0],
1595                         distorted_multiclass_scores_.shape[0])

2227       preprocessing_options = [(preprocessor.normalize_image, {

2229           'original_maxval': 255,
2230           'target_minval': 0,
2231           'target_maxval': 1
2232       })]

2343   def testRandomAbsolutePadImage(self):
2344     height_padding = 10
2345     width_padding = 20
2346     def graph_fn():
2347       images = self.createTestImages()
2348       boxes = self.createTestBoxes()
2349       labels = self.createTestLabels()
2350       tensor_dict = {
2351           fields.InputDataFields.image: tf.cast(images, dtype=tf.float32),
2352           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes: boxes,
2353           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_classes: labels,
2354       }
2355       preprocessing_options = [(preprocessor.random_absolute_pad_image, {
2356           'max_height_padding': height_padding,
2357           'max_width_padding': width_padding})]
2358       padded_tensor_dict = preprocessor.preprocess(tensor_dict,
2359                                                    preprocessing_options)
2360       original_shape = tf.shape(images)
2361       final_shape = tf.shape(padded_tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.image])
2362       return original_shape, final_shape
2363     for _ in range(100):
2364       original_shape, output_shape = self.execute_cpu(graph_fn, [])
2365       _, height, width, _ = original_shape
2366       self.assertGreaterEqual(output_shape[1], height)
2367       self.assertLess(output_shape[1], height + height_padding)
2368       self.assertGreaterEqual(output_shape[2], width)
2369       self.assertLess(output_shape[2], width + width_padding)

2386       preprocessing_options = [(preprocessor.random_absolute_pad_image, {
2387           'max_height_padding': height_padding,
2388           'max_width_padding': width_padding
2389       })]
2390       padded_tensor_dict = preprocessor.preprocess(tensor_dict,
2391                                                    preprocessing_options)
2392       original_shape = tf.shape(images)
2393       final_shape = tf.shape(padded_tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.image])
2394       padded_keypoints = padded_tensor_dict[
2395           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_keypoints]
2396       return (original_shape, final_shape, padded_keypoints)
2397     for _ in range(100):
2398       original_shape, output_shape, padded_keypoints_ = self.execute_cpu(
2399           graph_fn, [])
2400       _, height, width, _ = original_shape
2401       self.assertGreaterEqual(output_shape[1], height)
2402       self.assertLess(output_shape[1], height + height_padding)
2403       self.assertGreaterEqual(output_shape[2], width)
2404       self.assertLess(output_shape[2], width + width_padding)
2405       # Verify the keypoints are populated. The correctness of the keypoint
2406       # coordinates are already tested in random_pad_image function.
2407       self.assertEqual(padded_keypoints_.shape, (2, 3, 2))

3302   def testResizePadToMultipleWithMasks(self):
3303     """Tests resizing when padding to multiple with masks."""
3304     def graph_fn():
3305       image = tf.ones((200, 100, 3), dtype=tf.float32)
3306       masks = tf.ones((10, 200, 100), dtype=tf.float32)
3307 
3308       _, out_masks, out_shape = preprocessor.resize_pad_to_multiple(
3309           image, multiple=32, masks=masks)

3387   def testRandomSelfConcatImageVertically(self):
3388 
3389     def graph_fn():
3390       images = self.createTestImages()
3391       boxes = self.createTestBoxes()
3392       labels = self.createTestLabels()
3393       weights = self.createTestGroundtruthWeights()
3394       confidences = weights
3395       scores = self.createTestMultiClassScores()
3396 
3397       tensor_dict = {
3398           fields.InputDataFields.image: tf.cast(images, dtype=tf.float32),
3399           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_boxes: boxes,
3400           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_classes: labels,
3401           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_weights: weights,
3402           fields.InputDataFields.groundtruth_confidences: confidences,
3403           fields.InputDataFields.multiclass_scores: scores,
3404       }
3405 
3406       preprocessing_options = [(preprocessor.random_self_concat_image, {
3407           'concat_vertical_probability': 1.0,
3408           'concat_horizontal_probability': 0.0,

3411           True, True, True)

3413           tensor_dict, preprocessing_options, func_arg_map=func_arg_map)
3414 
3415       original_shape = tf.shape(images)[1:3]
3416       final_shape = tf.shape(output_tensor_dict[fields.InputDataFields.image])[
3417           1:3]

3718   def testConvertClassLogitsToSoftmax(self):
3719     def graph_fn():
3720       multiclass_scores = tf.constant(
3721           [[1.0, 0.0], [0.5, 0.5], [1000, 1]], dtype=tf.float32)
3722       temperature = 2.0
3723 
3724       converted_multiclass_scores = (
3725           preprocessor.convert_class_logits_to_softmax(
3726               multiclass_scores=multiclass_scores, temperature=temperature))
3727       return converted_multiclass_scores
3728     converted_multiclass_scores_ = self.execute_cpu(graph_fn, [])
3729     expected_converted_multiclass_scores = [[0.62245935, 0.37754068],
3730                                             [0.5, 0.5],
3731                                             [1, 0]]
3732     self.assertAllClose(converted_multiclass_scores_,
3733                         expected_converted_multiclass_scores)
3734 
3735   @parameterized.named_parameters(
3736       ('scale_1', 1.0),
3737       ('scale_1.5', 1.5),
3738       ('scale_0.5', 0.5)
3739   )
3740   def test_square_crop_by_scale(self, scale):
3741     def graph_fn():
3742       image = np.random.randn(256, 256, 1)
3743 
3744       masks = tf.constant(image[:, :, 0].reshape(1, 256, 256))
3745       image = tf.constant(image)
3746       keypoints = tf.constant([[[0.25, 0.25], [0.75, 0.75]]])
3747 
3748       boxes = tf.constant([[0.25, .25, .75, .75]])
3749       labels = tf.constant([[1]])
3750       label_weights = tf.constant([[1.]])
3751 
3752       (new_image, new_boxes, _, _, new_masks,
3753        new_keypoints) = preprocessor.random_square_crop_by_scale(
3754            image,
3755            boxes,
3756            labels,
3757            label_weights,
3758            masks=masks,
3759            keypoints=keypoints,
3760            max_border=256,
3761            scale_min=scale,
3762            scale_max=scale)
3763       return new_image, new_boxes, new_masks, new_keypoints
3764     image, boxes, masks, keypoints = self.execute_cpu(graph_fn, [])
3765     ymin, xmin, ymax, xmax = boxes[0]
3766     self.assertAlmostEqual(ymax - ymin, 0.5 / scale)
3767     self.assertAlmostEqual(xmax - xmin, 0.5 / scale)
3768 
3769     k1 = keypoints[0, 0]
3770     k2 = keypoints[0, 1]
3771     self.assertAlmostEqual(k2[0] - k1[0], 0.5 / scale)
3772     self.assertAlmostEqual(k2[1] - k1[1], 0.5 / scale)
3773 
3774     size = max(image.shape)
3775     self.assertAlmostEqual(scale * 256.0, size)
3776 
3777     self.assertAllClose(image[:, :, 0],
3778                         masks[0, :, :])
